--- a/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -10,9 +10,6 @@
 
 ### Changed
 
-* `global` does not use the unsafe-eval `new Function` trick anymore allowing to have CSP strict compliant packages with `wasm-bindgen`.
-  #[4910](https://github.com/wasm-bindgen/wasm-bindgen/pull/4910)
-
 ### Fixed
 
 ### Removed
